Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_report...lipping_report(25.10)    timing_report...lipping_report(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_enable_em_index_clipping_report

Syntax
       timing_report_enable_em_index_clipping_report {true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables index clipping reporting for EM (electro-migration) DRV (design
       rule violation) reports.

       For  more  information, refer to the "Cell EM Analysis and ECO" section
       in the Innovus User Guide.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

